#. type: Plain text
#: sections/expansion_content.tex:8
msgid ""
"\\pagetarget{Expansion Content} Numerous expansions have been released for "
"Heroes III: The Board Game, introducing new gameplay elements.  Most "
"expansion rules are integrated directly into the relevant sections of this "
"rulebook where they belong.  Below you'll find an overview of all expansion "
"content."
msgstr ""
"\\pagetarget{Expansion Content} Герои Меча и Магии III: Настольная Игра "
"имеет ряд дополнений, приносящих в игру новые игровые механики. Большинство "
"правил этих дополнений включены непосредственно в разделы этой книги. Ниже "
"вы найдете обзор состава дополнений, а также новые правила: как общие для "
"ряда дополнений, так и уникальные."

#. type: Plain text
#: sections/expansion_content.tex:25
msgid "\\textbf{The following contents are added by many of the expansions:}"
msgstr "\\textbf{Многие дополнения содержат следующие нововведения:}"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/expansion_content.tex:25
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "\\subsection*{\\pagetarget{Miniatures}{Unit Miniatures}}\n"
#| "If you want to play your Combats with Miniatures, place and move them over the Combat Board instead of the cards.\n"
#| "You can put Miniatures on top of the cards or keep the cards next to the Combat Board to form an initiative bar for better visualization of the order in which units activate.\\par\n"
#| "\\vspace*{1em}\n"
#| "If you play with Miniatures, there are a few rules to follow:\n"
#| "\\begin{itemize}\n"
#| "  \\item If any of the following occur during Combat with Neutral Units, discard the Neutral Unit card and draw another card in its place:\n"
#| "    \\begin{itemize}\n"
#| "      \\item if you draw the same Neutral Unit more than once,\n"
#| "      \\item if you draw any unit you already have in your army,\n"
#| "      \\item if you draw any unit from your Faction.\n"
#| "    \\end{itemize}\n"
#| "  \\item While you recruit Neutral Units, you cannot recruit any units from a Faction that is controlled by a player or any units that are already in any player's army.\n"
#| "  Discard that unit card and draw another.\n"
#| "\\end{itemize}\n"
#| "\n"
msgid ""
"{2}\n"
"\\subsection*{\\pagetarget{Miniatures}{Unit Miniatures}}\n"
"If you want to play your Combats with Miniatures, place and move them over the Combat Board instead of the cards.\n"
"You can put Miniatures on top of the cards or keep the cards next to the Combat Board to form an initiative bar for better visualization of the order in which units activate.\\par\n"
"If you play with Miniatures, there are a few rules to follow:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item If any of the following occur during Combat with Neutral Units, discard the Neutral Unit card and draw another card in its place:\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item if you draw the same Neutral Unit more than once,\n"
"      \\item if you draw any unit you already have in your army,\n"
"      \\item if you draw any unit from your Faction.\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\item While you recruit Neutral Units, you cannot recruit any units from a Faction that is controlled by a player or any units that are already in any player's army.\n"
"  Discard that unit card and draw another.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{\\pagetarget{Miniatures}{Миниатюры отрядов}}\n"
"Если вы хотите проводить сражения с миниатюрами, разместите их на доске сражений вместо карт.\n"
"Вы можете разместить карты под миниатюрами, либо разложить их возле доски сражений для формирования очереди ходов для лучшей визуализаци порядка активации отрядов.\\par\n"
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"При игре с миниатюрами есть несколько правил:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item Если в ходе сражения с нейтральными отрядами вы вытянули:\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item одинаковые карты нейтрального отряда, либо\n"
"      \\item карту отряда, который уже есть в вашей армии, либо\n"
"      \\item карту отряда вашей фракции\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\n"
"  сбросьте эту карту и возьмите новую.  \\item Во время найма нейтрального отряда вы не можете нанимать отряды из фракций других игроков, а также отряды, которыми уже владеет другой игрок.\n"
"  Сбросьте такую карту и возьмите новую.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

